","headword":"no parking"},{"type":"note","text":"◎no-parking zone禁止停车区"},{"type":"entry","text":"illegal parking 违章停车","headword":"illegal parking"},{"type":"entry","text":"traffic court 交通法庭","headword":"traffic court"},{"type":"entry","text":"license plate 牌照","headword":"license plate"},{"type":"entry","text":"missing [ˈmɪsɪŋ]","headword":"missing"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.丢失的"},{"type":"entry","text":"intentionally covered 故意遮挡（号牌）","headword":"intentionally covered"},{"type":"entry","text":"jaywalk [ˈdʒeɪwɔːk]","headword":"jaywalk"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.乱穿马路"}]},{"number":2118,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"traffic ticket 交通罚单","headword":"traffic ticket"},{"type":"entry","text":"motor vehicle inspection decal 机动车检验合格标志","headword":"motor vehicle inspection decal"}]},{"number":2119,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"unlicenced [ʌnˈlaɪsnst]","headword":"unlicenced"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.没有执照的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎unlicenced driver无执照的驾驶员"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Turn to the right, and you can see a pedestrian overpass at the"},{"type":"text","text":"intersection.（向右转，然后你会看到十字路口那有一座行人过街天"},{"type":"text","text":"桥。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Thank you very much. （非常感谢。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：If you jaywalk, you could easily get hit by the cars. （如果你乱穿"},{"type":"text","text":"马路就很容易被车撞到。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I know. It will not happen next time. （我知道。下次不会"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"}]}]}